    <description>Single intravenous dose of AT-III (Human) sufficient to achieve an absolute increase of 20% (percentage points) above pretreatment AT levels according the following formula:
AT-III (Human) dose (IU) required = (20) × (subject weight in kg) / 1.4</description>
  </arm_group>
